Incredible Intuition		KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Incredible Intuition	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DEFINE:IncredibleIntuitionTimes|0	DESC:The Eiring Guard adds the listed bonus to Sense Motive, Listen Spot and Search. Furthermore, they are capable of locating traps like a rogue, though they possess no ability to disarm them																																																	BONUS:VAR|IncredibleIntuitionTimes|(EiringGuardLVL+2/3)*5	SOURCEPAGE:p.	ASPECT:NAME|Incredible Intuition +%1|IncredibleIntuitionTimes
Unwavering Loyalty		KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Unwavering Loyalty	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality									DESC:The Eiring Guard cannot be persuaded, magically or otherwise to betray his employer. This does not render him immune to charm or compulsion, but does prevent the person from forcing the Eiring Guard to do anything in betrayal of his employer while under their influence.																																														SOURCEPAGE:p.
Detect Invisible			KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Detect Invisible		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality			DEFINE:DetectInvisibleTimes|0		DESC:The Eiring Guard may detect invisibility with a silent act of will as a supernatural ability as many times per day as noted on the table. This functions as the spell in all ways save for components.																																																BONUS:VAR|DetectInvisibleTimes|EiringGuardLVL+1/3		SOURCEPAGE:p.	ASPECT:NAME|Detect Invisible %1/day|DetectInvisibleTimes
Uncanny Dodge			KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Uncanny Dodge		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Uncanny Dodge									DESC:this functions as the rogue ability, and levels in this class stack with levels of rogue, or other classes with uncanny dodge, for this ability																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.
Find Secret Doors			KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Find Secret Doors	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality									DESC:Eiring Guards can locate secret doors as easily as an elf. This is not generally a duty of the class, but they are highly perceptive.																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.
Zone of Truth			KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Zone of Truth		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality									DESC:Once per day, the Eiring Guard can use a zone of truth as a spell like ability with a caster level equal to his Eiring Guard class level																																																																				SOURCEPAGE:p.	ASPECT:NAME|Zone of Truth 1/day
Deflect Attack			KEY:Eiring Guard ~ Deflect Attack		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Class Feature.Eiring Guard Class Feature.SpecialQuality									DESC:The Eiring Guard can deflect attacks as though he had that feat and combat reflexes. If he actually has both feats, he may deflect double the normal amount of attacks, or use AoO normally, plus as many deflections. He cannot use this ability to gain additional AoO in any other way. This virtual feat cannot be used unarmed																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.

